<plot>Bellflower is the story of the inhabitants of the historic Bellflower St. neighborhood. WOODROW and AIDEN, both best friends since childhood, are on the verge of completing a fully-functional, battle-ready flamethrower that they can own and love. Now all they need is a 'Mad Max' type ultra-fast muscle car, and a super-cool desert outlaw motorcycle. These are the last steps in achieving their ultimate goal - starting a post-apocalypse street gang called "Mother Medusa." After a promiscuous night on the town, the two end up at a local lounge where they meet MILLY and COURTNEY; a duo who will ultimately lead this group of twenty-somethings down a dark path of young love, betrayal, destruction and death. It is a ballad for every person who has ever loved and lost - with enough violence, weapons, battles, action, and sex, to truly tell a story where the stakes and emotions are much larger than the characters themselves.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?064720</url></doc>
